<p>I have a problem with environments about cache.</p>  <p>When I modified a Twig, I view this modification on DEV and I need clear cache for see this change on Prod. This is correct.</p>  <p>But when I modified a Controller, I view this modification on DEV and on PROD too, without clear cache.</p>  <p>I have this configuration on files:</p>  <p>app.php</p>  <pre><code>$kernel = new AppKernel('prod', false); </code></pre>  <p>app_dev.php</p>  <pre><code>$kernel = new AppKernel('dev', true); </code></pre>